Text: Thanks as always, even when I'm crap and don't post to say it :)

"Just" 200 more to go :)
I like the fact that they come unleashed now.

Oh, lest we forget:
Track #13 on MHRC 450 had severe audio problems (scratches on the CD?). Could we have a proper? It's Type O Negative - otherwise I wouldn't ask.
Another superb collection. Many thanks. T.
